               <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">
                  <p>Bearing in mind the high penetrating power of
              X-Rays, <list>
                        <item>Choose carefully the support/check also the back of the artwork to avoid
                  interferences.</item>
                        <item>Determine and mark carefully the security restricted area and define the
                  set-up geometry (X-ray beam direction) for safety of the operators and
                  public.</item>
                     </list>
                  </p>
